Performed OS upgrades and kernel patches on Ubuntu systems, ensuring minimal downtime and maintaining system stability in production environments.

Diagnosed and resolved boot disk and startup issues using Azure Serial Console and Boot Diagnostics during critical failure scenarios.

Developed and deployed a full monitoring and logging stack using Prometheus, Grafana, and Loki, enabling real-time system metrics, log aggregation, and custom alerting dashboards.

Configured and fine-tuned system logging and performance monitoring, improving visibility and proactive incident response.
